obj_root_law_sections_21_content:
  string
  line `(1) The Banking Companies (Acquisition and Transfer of Undertakings)`
  line `Ordinance, 1980 (3 of 1980), is hereby repealed.`
  line
  line `(2) Notwithstanding such repeal, anything done or any action taken, including any order made,`
  line `notification issued or direction given, under the said Ordinance shall be deemed to have been done, taken,`
  line `made, issued or given, as the case may be, under the corresponding provisions of this Act.`
obj_root_law_sections_21_footnotes:
  string
  line
